{"tid":826237,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打有留意fifa 係比利時唔比抽packs單新聞","createTime":"2018-09-18T06:04:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T14:02:01.000Z","uid":58089,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"de97471b7fe9aac3895feedaaebcd1e302764ebe","tid":826237,"uid":58089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T06:04:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GCqoE5DjOr4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGCqoE5DjOr4&d=JhsCm%2BJvmlA5Pvrt6R4333adZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=86eec562\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GCqoE5DjOr4</a><br />\n<br />\n大要:<br />\n比利時同荷蘭改左法例<br />\n話課金抽packs算係賭博行為，所以犯法<br />\n呢兩個國家有好多遊戲都取消左課金功能(overwatch, nba2k, csgo等等)<br />\n<br />\n但ea就拒絕，fifa繼續比人抽packs<br />\n最新發展好似係比利時同16個歐洲國家連手再做調查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遲下咁發展會唔會有一日fifa無得再課金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b918f5a4c312b9db36b9fcf07da1a7cd3612001","tid":826237,"uid":29080,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T06:07:40.000Z","msg":"抵啦"},{"pid":"2851b05b9232a41522a92c875693199362c1370d","tid":826237,"uid":135866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T06:16:08.000Z","msg":"之前Star Wars Battlefront 2 又係咁<br />\n跟住EA個股價係咁跌<br />\n今次又係咁真係唔知柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61c2f2210666ddc66b03ddba76a53b8332bc1ada","tid":826237,"uid":58089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T06:59:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34d84d283c0d4406862e660b05e24878d40e83f9","tid":826237,"uid":9430,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T07:01:46.000Z","msg":"fifa 仆街啦<br />\n死左 ut 就可以專心搞gameplay啦"},{"pid":"491914ec4232fadb754abe5e76466d3580754353","tid":826237,"uid":78666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T07:02